  <brief_title>Mid-term Effect Observation of Biodegradable Conduit Small Gap Tublization Repairing Peripheral Nerve Injury</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-center Study on Mid-term Effect Observation of Biodegradable Conduit Small Gap Tublization Repairing Peripheral Nerve Injury</official_title>
